title: MEET YOUR SPIRIT GUIDES (Guided Meditation) 528Hz
description:

Prepare your space so that you will not be interrupted.   Get into a comfortable position, preferably sitting.  Allow yourself to relax deeply and be guided into a beautiful garden, where you will meet and communicate with your spirit guide.

Written and spoken by Jess Shepherd
About The Speaker:
Jess Shepherd is an amazing Energy Therapist from the Gold Coast, Australia. She is a true blessing to this world and we know you will be able to FEEL her positive energy through these recordings. If you want to learn more from Jess or get in touch, please visit www.jessshepherd.com
or email us connectandcre8@gmail.com

*** How Can Guided Meditation help you? ***
Guided meditations are designed to bring you into a still and peaceful space, a relaxed but aware state where you are in sync with all that you want to attract into your life.

***This work is not intended to substitute for professional medical or counseling advice. If you suffer from a physical or mental illness, please always seek professional help.

***PLEASE do not listen to these tracks while operating machinery or driving. They are best used with headphones, lying in a comfortable, quiet place where you will not be disturbed.

We love creating guided meditations so please subscribe and share if you enjoy them.  With love and appreciation,
From Jess and the team at Rising Higher Meditation.
